                        <h3>For how long can I borrow a book?</h3>

                        <p>Books can be borrowed for 21 days. This period can be extended by one week at a time, with a maximum of two weeks. Extending is free of charge and can only be done if no one else made a reservation for that particular book. The status of your books can be checked on your personal library account on our website.</p>

                        <h3>How can I reserve a book?</h3>
                        <p>Search for the book via your personal library account on our website and click the "Reserve" button. A reservation is valid for 7 days. If the book is not picked up after 7 days, the reservation automatically be canceled by the Admin.</p>

                        <h3>What happens if I can't return a book on time?</h3>
                        <p>You can donate some books, or you can donate some amount (optional).</p>

